article_id:526,category_name:Important,title_name:Important: Regarding Save Data Backup ,image_path:,message:<div>Hello, everyone! It&#39;s the Dragalia Lost team here.</div><div><br></div><div>We would like to encourage you to link your Nintendo Account so you won&#39;t lose your Dragalia Lost progress if your device is unexpectedly lost or damaged. Here&#39;s some more information on linking your account.</div><div><br></div><div>■Linking an Account</div><div>By linking a Nintendo Account in advance, you can retrieve save data from Account Management when starting up the game if you switch or lose your device.</div><div><br></div><div>■Nintendo Account</div><div>This is a free-to-register account needed to back up save data for Nintendo smart device apps. If you do not have a Nintendo Account, you can create one by following the instructions in this link: <a href="https://accounts.nintendo.com">https://accounts.nintendo.com&nbsp;</a>.</div><div><br></div><div>■How to Link an Account In-Game</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/9bd85c9f259507007cbe66ddbfb4fad4.png"></div><div class="isShowIOS">For iOS devices:</div><div class="isShowIOS">1. Tap More on the in-game footer menu.</div><div class="isShowIOS">2. Tap Other.</div><div class="isShowIOS">3. Tap Account Management.</div><div class="isShowIOS">4. Tap Create/Link a Nintendo Account.</div><div class="isShowIOS">5. Tap Continue.</div><div class="isShowIOS">6. Tap Sign in.</div><div class="isShowIOS">7. Enter the ID and password for your Nintendo Account.</div><div class="isShowIOS">8. Tap Sign in.</div><div class="isShowIOS">9. Tap Select this person to finish linking your account.</div><div><br></div><div class="isShowAndroid">For Android devices:</div><div class="isShowAndroid">1. Tap More on the in-game footer menu.</div><div class="isShowAndroid">2. Tap Other.</div><div class="isShowAndroid">3. Tap Account Management.</div><div class="isShowAndroid">4. Tap Create/Link a Nintendo Account.</div><div class="isShowAndroid">5. Tap Sign In.</div><div class="isShowAndroid">6. Enter the ID and password for your Nintendo Account.</div><div class="isShowAndroid">7. Tap Sign In.</div><div class="isShowAndroid">8. Tap Select this person to finish linking your account.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. You can link only one Nintendo Account per save file.</div><div>2. You cannot switch the Nintendo Account linked to Dragalia Lost to another Nintendo Account.</div><div>3. For Nintendo Accounts linked to save data, should you link and play the game on a device with a different OS, any diamantium you have cannot be carried over to that device. The amount of diamantium you have will be stored on your original OS. If you link with the original OS again, you will be able to use your held diamantium again.</div><div>4. For more information about linking an account, select More on the in-game footer menu, then tap Help/Support, and see Nintendo Account under FAQ.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1561096800,update_time1561000110